ner>. How can we =E2=80=9Cstop=E2=80=9D the factorial at 5?</p>

<p>This is where permutations get cool: notice how we want to get rid of <m=
jx-container class=3D"MathJax CtxtMenu_Attached_0" jax=3D"SVG" tabindex=3D"=
0" ctxtmenu_counter=3D"2" style=3D"font-size: 95%; position: relative;"><sv=
